text: So nevermind about this. I reached out to Chris banes and according to him the target sdk value is ignored for libraries: <https://twitter.com/chrisbanes/status/630458646237986817?s=09>. I didn't know that.

attachments.fallback: <https://twitter.com/chrisbanes|@chrisbanes>: <https://twitter.com/aows|@aows> Any target SDK set by libraries are ignored. Only apps can define the target sdk (since any lib runs within the app).
